  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2583880/extras/78de60396683f0b377ecfe53aff8377d.avif?t=1721287330\" width=618 height=94 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2583880/extras/affe0c783d5476ec88c504e29f35c579.webp?t=1721287330\" width=618 height=30 /></span><br><br><strong>Unknown Dungeon</strong> is a rpg and rogue-like game with lots of interesting activities. From helping people in a village and doing guild quests to solving puzzles and fighting difficult bosses in the dungeon. Each player can find something fascinating to do.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2583880/extras/0d90283c2d76f26cf791e587110b04ef.poster.avif?t=1721287330\" width=618 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2583880/extras/0d90283c2d76f26cf791e587110b04ef.webm?t=1721287330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2583880/extras/0d90283c2d76f26cf791e587110b04ef.mp4?t=1721287330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2583880/extras/affe0c783d5476ec88c504e29f35c579.webp?t=1721287330\" width=618 height=30 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RPG Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Playable characters can be upgraded making them more effective<br></li><li>The game has interesting storyline with lots of quests and dialogues<br></li><li>Each character has its own abilities, weapons and combat styles<br></li><li>The world has lots of peaceful explorable areas as well as dangerous ones<br></li><li>The game has pretty complex combat system</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2583880/extras/330cb3fbafa93c22e4bca86eb6e21217.poster.avif?t=1721287330\" width=618 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2583880/extras/330cb3fbafa93c22e4bca86eb6e21217.webm?t=1721287330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2583880/extras/330cb3fbafa93c22e4bca86eb6e21217.mp4?t=1721287330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2583880/extras/affe0c783d5476ec88c504e29f35c579.webp?t=1721287330\" width=618 height=30 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rogue-like Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The dungeon has randomly generated floors with unique rooms and monsters<br></li><li>There are lots of playable characters presented in the game<br></li><li>The deeper you go in the dungeon the harder will be the enemies and the better loot you will get<br></li><li>The only things you can get out of the dungeon are experience and local currency<br></li><li>Some rooms may contain monsters, other — puzzles</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2583880/extras/aa279082e9663ca13f5ee21f92ad0a97.poster.avif?t=1721287330\" width=618 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2583880/extras/aa279082e9663ca13f5ee21f92ad0a97.webm?t=1721287330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2583880/extras/aa279082e9663ca13f5ee21f92ad0a97.mp4?t=1721287330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2583880/extras/affe0c783d5476ec88c504e29f35c579.webp?t=1721287330\" width=618 height=30 /></span>",
